{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861341963,"sessionID":"ses_2866b12a8ffeIHii9DrS9i1fWL","part":{"id":"prt_d7995632200134KWpstb0uhT6O","messageID":"msg_d799555e2001KRB2MMFsbi2CMU","sessionID":"ses_2866b12a8ffeIHii9DrS9i1fWL","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_9ee12067b9d544459122934a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-021 — CLI build 命令 Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: DockerService Enhancements\n\n- [ ] **T101** Add `check_docker_available()` method to `DockerService` that returns `bool`\n  - *Verify:* `python -c \"from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService; print(DockerService().check_docker_available())\"`\n\n- [ ] **T102** Add `build_image(dockerfile_path, context_path, image_name, tag, build_args)` method to `DockerService`\n  - *Verify:* Check method exists with correct signature\n\n- [ ] **T103** Add `get_image_info(image_name)` method to `DockerService`\n  - *Verify:* Check method exists with correct signature\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: BuildRuntime Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T201** Create `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` with `BuildRuntime` class\n  - *Verify:* `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime.build_runtime import BuildRuntime; print('ok')\"`\n\n- [ ] **T202** Implement `_validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path)` method\n  - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` for missing workspace/metadata, raises `RuntimeError` for Docker unavailable\n\n- [ ] **T203** Implement `_increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)` method\n  - *Verify:* Semver patch bump works correctly, fallback handles non-semver\n\n- [ ] **T204** Implement `_build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)` method\n  - *Verify:* Calls DockerService.build_image with correct args\n\n- [ ] **T205** Implement `_build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)` method\n  - *Verify:* Handles cloud provider delegation\n\n- [ ] **T206** Implement `_update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, build_result)` method\n  - *Verify:* Updates metadata with image info and saves\n\n- [ ] **T207** Implement main `build(workspace_path, **options)` method with version increment and rollback\n  - *Verify:* Full build flow works, version rolls back on failure\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: CLI Integration\n\n- [ ] **T301** Add `build` command to `agentcube/cli/main.py` Typer app\n  - *Verify:* `kubectl-agentcube build --help`\n\n- [ ] **T302** Implement `build` command options: `-f/--workspace`, `-p/--proxy`, `--cloud-provider`, `--output`, `--verbose`\n  - *Verify:* All options appear in `--help`\n\n- [ ] **T303** Connect `build` command to `BuildRuntime.build()` with error handling\n  - *Verify:* Error messages display correctly with `_handle_error`\n\n- [ ] **T304** Add success output with Rich formatting showing image name, size, build time\n  - *Verify:* Rich Panel displays with correct fields\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Testing\n\n- [ ] **T401** Write unit tests for `BuildRuntime._validate_build_prerequisites`\n  - *Verify:* `pytest tests/ -v -k \"test_validate\"`\n\n- [ ] **T402** Write unit tests for `BuildRuntime._increment_version`\n  - *Verify:* Tests pass for semver and non-semver versions\n\n- [ ] **T403** Write unit tests for `BuildRuntime._build_local`\n  - *Verify:* Mock DockerService, verify correct calls\n\n- [ ] **T404** Write integration test for `build` command end-to-end\n  - *Verify:* Full workflow with test workspace\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# CLI help\nkubectl-agentcube build --help\n\n# Basic build (requires packed workspace with metadata)\nkubectl-agentcube build -f /path/to/workspace\n\n# Build with proxy\nkubectl-agentcube build -f . -p http://proxy:8080\n\n# Build with cloud provider\nkubectl-agentcube build -f . --cloud-provider huawei\n\n# Run all tests\npytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v\n\n# Run lint\nruff check agentcube/\nruff format agentcube/\n\n# Run typecheck\nmypy agentcube/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Requires: AR-020 (pack command) completed\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` (pattern reference)\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Design stage ST-3 complete - implementation ready\n- Build mode defaults to \"local\" from metadata\n- Version increments before build, rolls back on failure\n- Cloud build delegates to provider (placeholder implementation)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/cli/main.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/docker_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775861341938,"end":1775861341959}}}}
